/* â”€â”€ Demo 55: Luxury Hotel â€” Grand RÃ©sidence â”€â”€ */
/* Palette: Deep Forest #0d1a0f / Champagne #e8d4a0 / Ivory #f8f4ec / Gold #c8a030 */
